{
  "texts": [
    "To begin with, we try introducing higher risk tolerance.",
    "We run the baseline streetlight experiment with riskloving agents, starting with one risk-loving agent and incrementing by one until all AI agents are risk-lovers.",
    "12 Since we are interested in the intensity of the streetlight effect, we once more focus only on the data condition where the ruby is revealed.",
    "We find that exploration monotonically increases with the number of risk-loving agents (Figure 6 Panel B), and consequently, more players are able to locate a breakthrough (Figure 6 Panel A).",
    "To verify that the risk endowment is working as intended, we review the agents' rationales, which are quite instructive."
  ]
}